{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/media-center/qcdc-celebrates-completion-of-first-edition-of-career-readiness-program","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"0b2a8dc2-cac7-5d04-9564-f3c39bd136b2","slug":"qcdc-celebrates-completion-of-first-edition-of-career-readiness-program","title":"QCDC Celebrates Completion of First Edition Of Career Readiness Program","date":"2019-05-11","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"2LTdoMooBa6w04sioQY2ue"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"925eb228-cc2f-5aa7-b56f-3ebdc8a9c88f","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Qatar Career Development Center (QCDC), a member of Qatar Foundation (QF), has wrapped up the first edition of its Career Readiness Program, which aims to enhance the delivery of career guidance services to students with mild to moderate learning challenges from Awsaj Academy, also a member of QF.</p>\n<p>Adapting the best international career guidance models into the local context, the program bolsters the confidence of students, creating more opportunities to grow their skills and help them make informed choices about their professional future. It also attempts to establish effective local career eco-systems and reshape society’s approach to education and learning.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"166fd59f-dd79-5a8a-9a87-473306cf71eb","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"91251dd4-a00e-53cc-80a7-2ce70644c553","title":"Image1 (008)","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":2252,"height":1501}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6d97ORko0buj30DkqOqvdr/ec4b8a031075ac5f753eee3af024db95/Image1__008_.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6d97ORko0buj30DkqOqvdr/ec4b8a031075ac5f753eee3af024db95/Image1__008_.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6d97ORko0buj30Dk