03_.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fit=pad 1540w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=2310&h=1290&q=85&fit=pad 2310w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=2314&h=1292&q=85&fit=pad 2314w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=385&h=215&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 385w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=770&h=430&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 770w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 1540w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=2310&h=1290&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 2310w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/54F0vxLSrJnI2o5Niq4mKn/eee5f8008545ec5190a28ae7bf35c20a/Image3__003_.jpg?w=2314&h=1292&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 2314w","sizes":"(max-width: 1540px) 100vw, 1540px"}}}]},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"1b623644-b0da-50c3-9d5d-e13d72292b4f","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The Career Readiness Program was piloted last year within the framework of a Memorandum of Understanding signed between QCDC and Awsaj Academy.</p>\n<p>The program featured weekly cross-structural interventions and project-based learning activities that have been integrated in the school’s curriculums. Activities included workshops, motivational talks by Qatari entrepreneurs, field trips to different industries, volunteering opportunities, and social responsibility projects that highlight the ethical values of the Qatari society, and connects the larger community with students.</p>\n<p>The program also featured practical internship opportunities. QCDC created individual internship plans that capitalized on the strengths and interests of students. The internships ran on a weekly basis, with tasks gradually increasing in complexity and intensity. </p>\n<p>Through such activities, the program empowers students to become active members of society by seeking career paths that align with QNV 2030, and contribute positively to the diversification of the Qatari economy.</p>"}}}]}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"2V7lsK5naIy62IfFywJyjL","languageCode":"en-US","alternateLanguage":"/ar/media-center/qcdc-celebrates-completion-of-first-edition-of-career-readiness-program","currSlug":"/media-center/qcdc-celebrates-completion-of-first-edition-of-career-readiness-program","title":"QCDC Celebrates Completion of First Edition Of Career Readiness Program"}}}